{"tid":2073383,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過返工講上司壞說話，返工唔開心都可分享下","createTime":"2020-06-21T09:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T17:16:37.000Z","uid":212953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2aeb6cc07b6844fe3cf58e670a283b8d140487","tid":2073383,"uid":212953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"如題，跟手俾人報串，隔兩日炒左<br />\nn年前既黎，是咁的<br />\n新工返左1個月到，唔係幾鐘意，同上司都唔夾，成個team得兩個人要日對夜對<br />\n主要覺得佢好廢，唔識就叫你做，做到啦又多聲多氣<br />\n話唔跟佢果套，重點係你都唔撚識又無講點做，踢條毛？<br />\n有次蛇出去同fd講電話，呻過下上司d衰野，話佢無料扮野<br />\n不過我無開名用代號稱呼咁<br />\n唔知俾邊條撚樣聽到報串，佢又知我講緊邊個<br />\n最尾俾上司捉左入房傾，我梗係死口唔認，有乜證據？<br />\n不過走左之後，成個人都開心好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩星期後搵過分工好d，人工又高d"},{"pid":"e25fc6f9123a04f320f0e5a25b419395d61747de","tid":2073383,"uid":90304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQDovqq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQDovqq.png&h=7e82c318&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ed5006ddc4467251d4b869e1923adc78cdb27cc","tid":2073383,"uid":212953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e25fc6f9123a04f320f0e5a25b419395d61747de","tid":2073383,"uid":90304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQDovqq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQDovqq.png&h=7e82c318&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"做護士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d032f48adbc3d7f138fe41686ca850fd566f4aef","tid":2073383,"uid":212953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T17:16:37.000Z","msg":"無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}